---
// 8. Math - exam math demo screen.
---
<section class="mathsec" id="math">
  <div class="container mathsec__inner">
    <div class="mathsec__content">
      <h2 class="mathsec__title" data-i18n="mathsec.title">Anyone can do the exam math, even if you have not done math in&nbsp;years</h2>
      <p class="mathsec__text" data-i18n="mathsec.text">Commissions, proration, LTV, area, taxes. Step by step, with each problem in your language. The app also teaches the basics, like percentages and fractions, and <strong>you review as you solve</strong>: every problem makes the skill behind it stronger.</p>
      <div class="library__badges">
        <span class="library__badge" data-i18n="mathsec.badge-commissions">Commissions</span>
        <span class="library__badge" data-i18n="mathsec.badge-percentages">Percentages and fractions</span>
        <span class="library__badge" data-i18n="mathsec.badge-area">Area</span>
        <span class="library__badge" data-i18n="mathsec.badge-taxes">Taxes and proration</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mathsec__phone">
      <div class="phone-cased">
        <img src="/pics/phone-clean.svg" alt="" class="phone__shell" />
        <div class="phone__frame phone__frame--hero">
          <iframe data-src="/screens/Math%20Problem%20Screen.html" title="Демо: математика экзамена - задача с переводом, разбором и практикой" style="width:100%; height:100%; border:none; display:block;" scrolling="no"></iframe>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
